abstract: Google says mobile is a multi-billion dollar business, but some analysts wonder whether cellphone users will ever click on ads the same way the do on computers.
snippet: Google says mobile is a multi-billion dollar business, but some analysts wonder whether cellphone users will ever click on ads the same way the do on computers.
lead_paragraph: Google's earnings report Thursday highlighted its mobile business's growing contribution to revenue. But can mobile ever be as big a business as desktop search?

headline.main: Can Mobile Search Be as Big for Google as Desktop Search?
